asset.hookText: Hi Kyle. We saw your review on Amazon. From your description, it sounds like the Dirt Water Tank on your FloorMate Deluxe may have just gotten full. We put together a quick video to show you what that looks like and sounds like. A quick dump of the tank, and you should be on your way again! Let us know if this doesn't fix the problem for you. We're always here to help. -Felicia
